<li><p><strong>Usage:</strong> It is typically used under the guidance of healthcare professionals, especially for infants, children, or adults with severe food allergies, malabsorption issues, or certain medical conditions.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Prescription:</strong> Neocate Splash may be available by prescription, and its use should be supervised by healthcare providers to ensure proper dosing and monitoring.</p></li>
</ul>

